ll press to emphasize triceps and inner chest","Maintain constant tension by keeping the dumbbells close together throughout the movement","Use a controlled tempo with a 2-3 second lowering phase for optimal muscle activation","Start with lighter weight than your regular dumbbell press as this variation is more challenging","Avoid letting the dumbbells drift apart during the movement to maintain proper form"],"muscleGroup":"chest","secondaryMuscles":null,"equipment":"dumbbell","category":"Chest","difficulty":"intermediate","videoDurationSecs":null,"hasVideo":true,"hasVideoWhite":false,"hasVideoGym":true,"exerciseType":["strength"],"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0/play_720p.mp4?token=UHx2UxrhSx2lBU5EDQwSIw&token_path=%2F0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0/playlist.m3u8?token=UHx2UxrhSx2lBU5EDQwSIw&token_path=%2F0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0?library=clean","videos":[{"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0/play_720p.mp4?token=UHx2UxrhSx2lBU5EDQwSIw&token_path=%2F0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0/playlist.m3u8?token=UHx2UxrhSx2lBU5EDQwSIw&token_path=%2F0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/0bcda946-15ae-4db6-ac47-b5518a4cfce0?library=clean","tag":"gym-shot","orientation":"portrait","isPrimary":true},{"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/ba2e4c73-fa37-45ad-9cd9-ae691ca4019a/play_720p.mp4?token=-VqCO-gcVbSABmCwktXrfQ&token_path=%2Fba2e4c73-fa37-45ad-9cd9-ae691ca4019a%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/ba