cles","Start with a lower elevation if you're new to declined push-ups and gradually increase the height","Stop immediately if you experience any wrist, shoulder, or lower back discomfort"],"muscleGroup":"chest","secondaryMuscles":null,"equipment":"bodyweight","category":"Chest","difficulty":"intermediate","videoDurationSecs":null,"hasVideo":true,"hasVideoWhite":true,"hasVideoGym":false,"exerciseType":["strength","calisthenics"],"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/b2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf/play_720p.mp4?token=W-rG7aQqO-8xIgfckEssOA&token_path=%2Fb2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/b2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf/playlist.m3u8?token=W-rG7aQqO-8xIgfckEssOA&token_path=%2Fb2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/b2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf?library=clean","videos":[{"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/b2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf/play_720p.mp4?token=W-rG7aQqO-8xIgfckEssOA&token_path=%2Fb2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/b2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf/playlist.m3u8?token=W-rG7aQqO-8xIgfckEssOA&token_path=%2Fb2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/b2703fec-ae86-4e02-b132-86b9db729fcf?library=clean","tag":"white-background","orientation":"landscape","isPrimary":true}]},{"id":"2930d41f-177c-4f36-bd91-4867afb85a3b","title":"Dips","slug":"dips","description":"Starting position: Grip parallel bars or the edge of a sturdy bench with arms fully extended, supporting your body weight with feet off the ground or extended forward. Execution: Lower your body by bending your elbows until your shoulders drop below your elbows, then press back up to the starting position.","instructions":["Grip parallel bars, arms straight","Lower body by bending elbows","Go until upper arms parallel or comfortable depth","Push up to starting position"],"importantPoints":["Lean forward for more chest, upright for more triceps","Don't go too deep (shoulder strain)","Control the descent","Full lockout at top","Add weight when bodyweight is easy"],"muscleGroup":"chest","secondaryMuscles":null,"equipment":"bodyweight","category":"Push","difficulty":null,"videoDurationSecs":null,"hasVideo":true,"hasVideoWhite":true,"hasVideoGym":false,"exerciseType":["strength","calisthenics"],"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4/play_720p.mp4?token=aBI1PrKsMEHZBLEXeAKSHw&token_path=%2F0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4/playlist.m3u8?token=aBI1PrKsMEHZBLEXeAKSHw&token_path=%2F0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4?library=clean","videos":[{"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4/play_720p.mp4?token=aBI1PrKsMEHZBLEXeAKSHw&token_path=%2F0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4/playlist.m3u8?token=aBI1PrKsMEHZBLEXeAKSHw&token_path=%2F0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/0ecab2ea-2d8b-40a8-837c-7bd078dc94d4?library=clean","tag":"white-background","orientation":"landscape","isPrimary":true}]},{"id":"60ec7728-577b-4dea-a5e9-4b8ac16b6038","title":"Dips - Triceps Version","slug":"dips-triceps-version","description":"Starting position: Sit on the floor with legs extended, hands placed on the ground beside your hips gripping a stable surface or handles, supporting your body weight on your arms. Execution: Lower your body by bending your elbows, then press back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","instructions":["Position yourself sitting on the floor with legs extended straight in front of you","Place your hands on the ground or grip handles beside your hips, fingers pointing forward","Support your body weight on your arms with shoulders directly over your hands","Lower your body by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides","Descend until you feel a stretch in your triceps or chest","Press through your palms to straighten your arms and return to starting position"],"importantPoints":["Keep your core engaged throughout the movement to maintain proper posture","Control the descent - avoid dropping down too quickly","Keep your shoulders down and back, avoiding hunching forward","Focus on using your triceps and chest muscles rather than momentum","If too difficult, bend your knees or place feet on the ground for assistance"],"muscleGroup":"chest","secondaryMuscles":null,"equipment":"bodyweight","category":"Chest","difficulty":"intermediate","videoDurationSecs":null,"hasVideo":true,"hasVideoWhite":true,"hasVideoGym":false,"exerciseType":["strength","calisthenics"],"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0/play_720p.mp4?token=Ps0lriFTtsL53XPjq0Yt5w&token_path=%2F2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0/playlist.m3u8?token=Ps0lriFTtsL53XPjq0Yt5w&token_path=%2F2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0%2F&expires=1781159178","thumbnailUrl":"https://exercise-api.ymove.app/api/v2/thumbnail/2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0?library=clean","videos":[{"videoUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0/play_720p.mp4?token=Ps0lriFTtsL53XPjq0Yt5w&token_path=%2F2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766e09c0%2F&expires=1781159178","videoHlsUrl":"https://vz-cfbc9d86-eae.b-cdn.net/2bbbd0e3-cb9c-4847-8b58-ef1e766